        "scorecard": "## Pre-Output Self-Audit Scorecard\n`Pillar 1 — TEXT INTEGRITY: PASS — Counted 28 original-language word occurrences; all 28 follow canonical form. Interlinear has 7 rows × 7 columns (MT) and 7 rows × 8 columns (LXX); all 49+56=105 cells filled.`\n`Pillar 2 — COVERAGE: PASS — All of Gen 1:1 treated in Single-Block Mode.`\n`Pillar 3 — HERMENEUTIC FIDELITY: PASS — Sensus Literalis applied per Difficult-Text discipline for Gen 1-11; no deep time.`\n`Pillar 4 — CANONICAL DEPTH: PASS — Motif trajectory to Col 1:16 terminus; loci tagged; Tripartite Synthesis complete.`\n`Pillar 5 — APPLICATION + DOXOLOGY: PASS — FCF to Doxology structure complete; indicative grounds imperative.`\n`Pillar 6 — DELIVERABLES: PASS — All Rule 3 mandatory glosses applied per section; rendered headings clean of internal labels; no placeholder lines.`\n",
